                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1596566425881-tip-3--save-on-textbooks" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#ca8c1cb7-814a-4619-a49d-50bba927d30e" href="#accordion-content-1596566425881-tip-3--save-on-textbooks" aria-controls="accordion-content-1596566425881-tip-3--save-on-textbooks" aria-expanded="false">
                            Tip 3: Save on textbooks
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1596566425881-tip-3--save-on-textbooks" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1596566425881-tip-3--save-on-textbooks">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1596566425881 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="da88fcfd-6a34-438d-85da-6f585cf65b5c" >

    <p>Buying brand new textbooks can be expensive, but there are ways to save. Digital textbooks are often cheaper. There are also used bookstores near campus, and many textbook groups on various social media platforms (such as Facebook) where you can buy and trade used textbooks.</p> 
<p>The Ryerson Library has a program called the <a href="https://library.ryerson.ca/services/borrower/textbook-collection/" target="_blank">Textbook Collection<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, opens in new window</span></a> that allows students to take out their textbooks for a short-term loan for many textbooks.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#da88fcfd-6a34-438d-85da-6f585cf65b5c");});</script></div>

