                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1596566447786-tip-5--part-time-work" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#ca8c1cb7-814a-4619-a49d-50bba927d30e" href="#accordion-content-1596566447786-tip-5--part-time-work" aria-controls="accordion-content-1596566447786-tip-5--part-time-work" aria-expanded="false">
                            Tip 5: Part-time work
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1596566447786-tip-5--part-time-work" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1596566447786-tip-5--part-time-work">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1596566447786 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="52bd9fbb-1cfd-4f25-8815-94280ceef5c3" >

    <p>If your schedule allows it, it is helpful to have a part-time job on top of your school schedule. If you apply for OSAP or other government student financial assistance, this typically isn’t enough to cover all your educational expenses and living costs, so it’s helpful to have the extra income to cover costs.</p> 
<p>Ryerson has an on-campus job program called <a href="/content/ryerson/student-financial-assistance/student-employment.html">Career Boost</a>. Career Boost provides full-time undergraduate students with the opportunity to work part-time on campus. The benefit with working on campus is that most employers are very flexible, which means you can spend that four hour break between classes earning some money!</p> 
<p>There are also full-time Career Boost positions available during the spring/summer semester.</p> 
<p>You can also reach out to the <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/career/">Career and Co-op Centre</a>, they can help you find off-campus work as well.&nbsp;</p>
    





</div>
